Gaupol 0.24
===========

 [X] Use a floating label for the statusbar
 [X] Show search dialog messages in a floating label
     in the search dialog
 [X] Use inline toolbars in the preferences dialog
     - https://wiki.gnome.org/Design/HIG/InlineToolbars
 [X] Apply GNOME Goal: Add keywords to application desktop files
     - https://wiki.gnome.org/GnomeGoals/DesktopFileKeywords
 [X] Remove video toolbar (video file and framerate selectors)
 [X] Hide translation text column by default and show only when a
     translation file is opened or the column is explicitly selected
     to be shown
 [ ] Clarify "select video" vs. "load video"?
 [ ] Add framerate selector to save dialogs?
 [X] Add Galician translation (Leandro Regueiro)

